  <brief_title>The Use of Intermittent Pneumatic Compression Device for Symptomatic Relief in Patients With Post Thrombotic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Use of Intermittent Pneumatic Compression Device for Symptomatic Relief in Patients With Post Thrombotic Syndrome</official_title>
