  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The use of ActiveCare+S.F.T 3rd generation (an Intermittent Pneumatic Compression Device)
      will improve quality of life in patients suffering from Post Thrombotic Syndrome compared to
      compression stockings which is the current gold standard of care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
